c: 30
v: 40
t: Tuhanku sidroe nyang peujeut gata í Raseuki gata pih ka Neukeubah ‘Oh lheuh nyan mate teuh bandum gata Udep lom teuma Neubri le Allah Toh Tuhan gata nyang peugot meunan Nyang ek peugot nyan nyang bukon Allah Hana meubacut pih ek jipeugot Meu kon Hadharat nyang Maha Murah Maha suci that Droeuneuh Manyang that Nibak charikat lagee jih peugah